<h3>Frenchi's Deli: Making Sandwiches Great Again</h3>
<p>Although Frenchi's Deli has been on campus for only 2 years, it has quickly made a name for itself. From the incredible sanwiches to the unbeatable customer service, Frenchi's has become a staple for many of the residents of South Oakland, myself included. If you have not expereinced Frenchi's for yourself, you are truly missing out on great food and great people.</p>

<p><a href="http://frenchisdeli.net/">Frenchi's Deli</a>, opened in 2014, is located at the corner of <a href=https://www.google.com/maps/place/449+Atwood+St,+Pittsburgh,+PA+15213/@40.4371065,-79.9548691,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x8834f18882ec3cef:0x3b9c53617321dca2!8m2!3d40.4371024!4d-79.9526804">Atwood and Dawson Street</a>. While it bears the name deli, Frenchi's has anything a resident of South Oakland could need. The business' motto? "If we don't have it, you don't need it." While it offers anything you could need, there are two huge reasons people continue to come back: the mouthwatering sandwiches and Frenchi himself.

If you're a first time Frenchi's customer, getting a sandwich is a must. The <a href="http://www.allmenus.com/pa/pittsburgh/502374-frenchis-deli/menu/">menu</a> has a wide variety of sandwiches, but one of the best sellers is the Le Frenchi's Chicken and Steak Combo, commmonly referred to as the Le Frenchi. However, you really can't go wrong when ordering at Frenchi's. Not only does the food taste great, the portions are generous as well. 

